==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: pit stop
<hw>pit" stop`</hw> <pr>(p⟦icr⟧t" st⟦ocr⟧p`)</pr> <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Auto Racing)</fld> <def>A stop by one of the competing
cars in a <it>pit</it> by the side of the racetrack, to take on
gasoline, change tires, or perform other maintenance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>Any pause in a journey, to
eat or drink, or to use a rest room.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A place where one may make a <er>pit stop</er>[1 or
2].</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pitt diamond</ent>⟦br⟧
